               <p>Before Lord Chief Justice Abbott.</p>
               <p>789. 
               <persName id="t18270405-36-defend273" type="defendantName">
                  ROBERT 
                  SMITH
               <interp inst="t18270405-36-defend273" type="surname" value="SMITH"></interp>
